graph TB
    Rider["Rider<br/>(Request Ride)"]
    Driver["Driver<br/>(Online)"]

    RideAPI["Ride API<br/>(Request)"]
    Matching["Matching Service<br/>(Algorithm)"]
    Location["Location Service<br/>(Geohashing)"]
    Pricing["Pricing Service<br/>(Surge)"]
    Payment["Payment Service"]
    Notification["Notification<br/>(WebSocket)"]

    RideDB["Ride Database<br/>(Ride State)"]
    LocationDB["Location Cache<br/>(Redis)"]
    Rating["Rating Service"]

    Rider -->|Request| RideAPI
    RideAPI --> Pricing
    RideAPI --> Matching
    Matching --> Location
    Location --> LocationDB
    Location -->|Find nearby drivers| Driver
    Matching -->|Match found| Notification
    Notification -->|Offer| Driver
    Driver -->|Accept| RideDB
    RideAPI --> Payment
    RideDB --> Rating

    style Matching fill:#4A90E2,stroke:#2E5C8A,color:#fff
    style Location fill:#50E3C2,stroke:#2D8A78,color:#fff
    style Pricing fill:#F5A623,stroke:#C17F1A,color:#fff
    style Notification fill:#BD10E0,stroke:#8B0A9D,color:#fff
